✓ DECISION: CSV Template is generated from the live schema, not hardcoded.
Accessible via the "CSV Template" button in the Schema Manager header. Shows only active fields.
✓ DECISION: The template builder modal allows field selection before download.
Required fields are pre-checked. Three quick-select buttons: Select All, Required Only, Clear.
✓ DECISION: Downloaded CSV includes three sections:

Header row — selected column names
Sample data row — realistic example values per field type
Enum reference block — comment rows listing all allowed values for any ENUM fields selected

